{"prompt": "Generate a website for a e-commerce store. The website should be elegant and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Elegant E-commerce Store</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #0d47a1; /* Dark Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #1976d2; /* Medium Blue */\n            --accent-color: #90caf9; /* Light Blue */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --bg-color: #f5f5f5;\n            --card-bg: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            background-color: var(--bg-color);\n            color: #333;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        header .container {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .logo {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            margin-left: 25px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: 500;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero-section {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            min-height: 400px;\n        }\n\n        .hero-content h1 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n        }\n\n        .hero-content p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #64b5f6; /* Lighter shade of accent */\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        .products-section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n        }\n\n        .products-section h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 50px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .product-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .product-card {\n            background-color: var(--card-bg);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            overflow: hidden;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        .product-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n\n        .product-image {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            background-color: var(--accent-color); /* Placeholder color */\n        }\n\n        .product-info {\n            padding: 20px;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n\n        .product-title {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .product-price {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .product-description {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: #666;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n        }\n\n        .add-to-cart-button {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 10px 15px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            align-self: flex-start; /* Align to the left */\n        }\n\n        .add-to-cart-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            opacity: 0.8;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"logo\">ELEGANCE</div>\n            <nav>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><a href=\"#\">Home</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#\">Shop</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#\">About</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#\">Contact</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero-section\">\n        <div class=\"container hero-content\">\n            <h1>Discover Timeless Style</h1>\n            <p>Curated collections for the modern connoisseur.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Shop Now</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"products-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Featured Products</h2>\n            <div class=\"product-grid\">\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/808080/ffffff?text=Product+1\" alt=\"Product 1\" class=\"product-image\">\n                    <div class=\"product-info\">\n                        <div>\n                            <h3 class=\"product-title\">Sophisticated Silk Scarf</h3>\n                            <p class=\"product-price\">$75.00</p>\n                            <p class=\"product-description\">A luxurious silk scarf, perfect for adding a touch of elegance to any outfit. Hand-finished with exquisite detail.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <button class=\"add-to-cart-button\">Add to Cart</button>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/808080/ffffff?text=Product+2\" alt=\"Product 2\" class=\"product-image\">\n                    <div class=\"product-info\">\n                        <div>\n                            <h3 class=\"product-title\">Classic Leather Handbag</h3>\n                            <p class=\"product-price\">$195.00</p>\n                            <p class=\"product-description\">Crafted from the finest full-grain leather, this timeless handbag offers both style and functionality.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <button class=\"add-to-cart-button\">Add to Cart</button>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/808080/ffffff?text=Product+3\" alt=\"Product 3\" class=\"product-image\">\n                    <div class=\"product-info\">\n                        <div>\n                            <h3 class=\"product-title\">Minimalist Silver Watch</h3>\n                            <p class=\"product-price\">$120.00</p>\n                            <p class=\"product-description\">An understated yet striking silver watch with a clean dial and reliable quartz movement. A statement of refined taste.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <button class=\"add-to-cart-button\">Add to Cart</button>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/808080/ffffff?text=Product+4\" alt=\"Product 4\" class=\"product-image\">\n                    <div class=\"product-info\">\n                        <div>\n                            <h3 class=\"product-title\">Elegant Pearl Earrings</h3>\n                            <p class=\"product-price\">$90.00</p>\n                            <p class=\"product-description\">Classic pearl stud earrings, lustrous and refined. The perfect accessory for any occasion, adding a touch of subtle luxury.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <button class=\"add-to-cart-button\">Add to Cart</button>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Elegance E-commerce. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Designed with <a href=\"#\">Elegance</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic JS for future interactivity (e.g., adding to cart)\n        document.querySelectorAll('.add-to-cart-button').forEach(button => {\n            button.addEventListener('click', function() {\n                alert('Item added to cart!');\n                // In a real application, you would update a cart state here.\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}